From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


This category is not shown on its member pages unless the appropriate user preference (Appearance → Show hidden categories) is set.
Articles which include mark-up for a microformat (or a component of a microformat). See the microformats project for background (note: articles using infoboxes or taxoboxes which generate a microformat will not be listed here; see Category:Templates generating microformats).
